      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight">API-First Businesses Built for Agent Consumers</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">The next generation of businesses will not be built for human users first. They will be built API-first, designed for agent consumers from day one. The interface is the API. The documentation is the product. The customer is a machine.</p>
